    "• WiC (Pilehvar and Camacho-Collados, 2019).",
    "The WiC dataset functions as a lexical disambiguation task, posing a binary classification challenge in the context of sentence pairs.",
    "Tasking the model with evaluating two text segments and a word occurring in both sentences, the objective is to discern whether the word holds identical meanings in the given contexts.",
